<font face=Arial size=-1 color=black><div class=titlebar>Level 8</div>

<div class=itemtext>The most serious bug in Sonic Brick is in Level 7. Although the level plays normally, it doesn't end when you clear all the bricks. To get the code for level 8, use the password for level 7, but add 1 from the first digit, add 6 to the second digit, add 7 to the third digit, and subtract 3 from the last digit.<br><br></div></font></td></tr></table>

