<div class=itemtext><center><br><img src=/sonichq/images/screenshots/fangames/sonicbrick/brick4.gif></center>

<p>This is tough! The metal bars constantly move up and down, and it's very diffeicult to get Sonic into the upper area where Robotnik is. Robotnik plays dirty this time - he tries to knock Tails out by letting bricks fall on him! If Tails is hit, he'll be stunned for quite a while, and it's almost guaranteed that Sonic will fall off the screen when this happens.<br><br></div></font></td></tr></table>

